340
00:21:41,810 --> 00:21:43,120
Right now,

341
00:21:43,660 --> 00:21:45,990
I've turned the key hidden piece

342
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:48,220
face up for you to see.

343
00:21:49,230 --> 00:21:51,590
Do you still think

344
00:21:51,790 --> 00:21:53,590
I would back down?

345
00:22:24,660 --> 00:22:25,550
General Lu,

346
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:28,420
let me remind you of one thing:

347
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:33,240
the Imperial Preceptor is sacred and untouchable.

348
00:22:34,360 --> 00:22:36,820
The last Imperial Preceptor had a secret affair

349
00:22:37,540 --> 00:22:39,660
