392
00:24:46,030 --> 00:24:46,810
All right.

393
00:24:47,310 --> 00:24:48,380
You may go for now.

394
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:49,770
Yes, Your Majesty.

395
00:24:54,720 --> 00:24:55,810
Put someone on him.

396
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:57,620
Check everyone

397
00:24:58,110 --> 00:24:59,490
