00:31:48,510 --> 00:31:50,490
you told Zhong Lin to bring him here.

498
00:31:51,520 --> 00:31:54,050
Luo Xianxue helped Hongqing save Shi Yan.

499
00:31:54,790 --> 00:31:55,700
I think

