00:38:55,880 --> 00:38:58,460
Imperial Preceptor Du has prepared Tusu wine for everyone.

564
00:38:58,960 --> 00:39:00,460
Let's all raise a toast

565
00:39:00,480 --> 00:39:01,650
to Great Qi's future,

566
00:39:01,670 --> 00:39:02,860
with fair winds and timely rain,

567
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:05,090
and a peaceful, prosperous people!

568
00:39:10,670 --> 00:39:11,610
How could this cup of wine

569
00:39:12,280 --> 00:39:13,610
possibly go

570
00:39:14,030 --> 00:39:15,380
